            It has been widely reported
<TIMEX TYPE="DATE">that Seven Years</TIMEX> in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Tibet</ENAMEX> , the tale of <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">Austrian</ENAMEX> mountaineer Heinrich
