foreshadowing of <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">Chinese</ENAMEX> atrocities (as reflected by a dream in which the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">Dalai</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Lama</ENAMEX> sees his native village being pillaged and monks shot) reflects the
